Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:07.90,flashback_br,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(300,0)}9年前 高仓家·起居室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.61,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}台风之夜。阳毬发高烧 很严重。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.62,0:00:07.90,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}打电话给医院也只被冷冷地敷衍了。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型台风13号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从本州沿太平洋北上 现正经过关东地区
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:18.86,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}西东京 中野区 杉并区 练马区
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.98,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}现在 请小心防范强风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救护车全部都派出去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们家也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿的烧退不了啊 这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的…?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠叶! 回来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个蠢材…!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠叶!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:02.25,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}くるくるまわる　君の瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:05.07,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}探してまわる　駅のホーム
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:10.16,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}響くファンファーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:13.36,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ガラガラ音をたてる街
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:16.27,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}とりあえず　耳を貸してみたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:22.73,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もうすぐ　消えるはずの世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:28.15,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:36.98,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もう二度と会えないような　そんな気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:39.35,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}運命が笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:44.71,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}臨界点を突破してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:47.51,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}限界ならすでに去って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:52.84,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}絶対的支配だって　崩壊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:58.73,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}終末理論は机上の　空論でしかないって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:09.29,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}0と1の世界線の果てから　叫ぶよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:17.91,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もうすぐ　君が会いに来るような気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:23.44,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕は目を閉じるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:12.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:02.25,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}转啊转 你的眼睛不停转
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:05.07,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在月台四处寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:10.16,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}号角声在空中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:13.36,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}大街上轰轰作响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:16.27,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}总之 先倾听这声音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:22.73,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在这个就要消逝的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:28.15,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:36.98,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}总是觉得 我们无法再度相会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:39.35,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}命运也在嘲笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:44.71,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}突破临界点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:47.51,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}极限已然消去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:52.84,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}就算被绝对地支配 也让它崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:58.73,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}末日理论无非是一纸空谈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:09.29,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在0与1的世界线的尽头 呼喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:17.91,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}总是觉得 你即将来与我相会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:23.44,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那我 就闭上眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查结果很稳定 身体情况也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样再观察一段时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不该这么说 不过这真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干我们这行的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会遇上极少数的病例 只能用奇迹来形容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹的情况正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于奇迹 我还有话想跟您说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能检查一下这个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好 这个就是在阳毬身上发生奇迹的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是我的推测…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个帽子的真身是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 是外星生命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个外星生命 用某种力量把阳毬的病…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 这也有道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是吗…!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个很有趣的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 很有趣 这是很好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是笑啊 「笑」!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑能增强免疫力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在医学领域里也很重视其效果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个帽子是从外星球来的啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样让你妹妹每天都开怀大笑吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌 得赶紧碾碎掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想工作的事情对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托阿佐美小姐你做这么难办的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是夏芽小姐的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那起事故 真是不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你说除了知道有人推你下去 其他都不记得了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上… 那时候的事 我记不太清了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在出事之前 我好像看到了什么人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了! 那个时候那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 看到那个了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏芽…小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是前几天 在地铁站内手扶梯上发生意外的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久宝阿佐美小姐的后续报道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据最新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久宝小姐对事故发生前后的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上是她对警方提问做出的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方还在收集目击者等相关信息 调查仍在进行当中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.73,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}早上好 我是云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:41.53,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我是光莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:43.26,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我们两人合起来就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:44.96,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Double Mayonname（注：mayonnaise+name的合成词）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:46.99,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}搞错啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.11,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我们两人合起来就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.99,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Double Mayonnamassage（mayonnaise+name+message的合成词）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.81,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不是这样的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 今天有什么事呢 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上呢…冠叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 事情来得很突然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 说是要卖掉这座房子 但也不是马上就怎样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 叔叔也会对你们负责 好好想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄养你们的亲戚那里 我也会打好招呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过三人一起住可能就不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是病人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 还没泡茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家会照顾好阳毬的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事情会马上告诉你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不想这么说…冠叶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的父母…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不会再回来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱我会筹来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多少钱才能不卖掉这个家?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠叶 再怎么说我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的 这不是你能筹到的数额啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要多少!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天跟爸爸约会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经不是小孩子了 感觉有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一句 我还没跟爸爸提起过「他」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为爸爸会吃醋的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我现在 还想继续做爸爸最心爱的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海鲜咖喱午饭两份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸吃这个可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南极特制芭菲 上面还有企鹅玩偶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那个也要一份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 改天再去那个水族馆玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那个水族馆」?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 跟妈妈一起三人经常去的 那个池袋的水族馆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸说企鹅的列队行进很有趣 就把头伸出通道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果不是被工作人员大骂了一顿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的…么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是还嚷着要亲子三人配 所以买了一样的企鹅手机链吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 确实是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为苹果很喜欢企鹅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:08:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸那时说 「苹果 这就好像专门为你做的…」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 现在跟女儿在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是定期的见面日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 晚上跟你吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话 让你的女儿小蓝也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人一样的手机链…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的「咖喱日」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己做的咖喱 给多蕗吃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的任务还不算结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 接下来要给多蕗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 Merci
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.69,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}注：法语「谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的路上 带着栗子蛋糕当礼物 去造访多蕗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗很喜欢吃栗子蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而拿着这个去的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定会令他陶醉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这里的 才是我心目中的「The Best of 栗子蛋糕」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗你真是fabulous max!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这味道…哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人陶醉啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 好像被人盯着一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:10:00.71,flashback_br,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(300,0)}9年前 暴风雨之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:58.50,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}那个时候冠叶发生了什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:00.71,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}爸爸呢? 阳毬呢? 家人会变成什么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸爸…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.47,slogan,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1072,253)}请有计划{\fs35}地{\fs55}使用。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.47,slogan,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(1069,284)}注意{\fs18}不要{\fs25}使用{\fs18}过度。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱已收到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠回来得好晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不跟我们联系 到底在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计又是和女孩子在厮混吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「要被花花公子冠叶菌传染啦」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是正是 辛辛苦苦做的饭都要凉掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我们先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 荻野目同学回家太晚也不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我妈妈经常加班 很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不~是 是根本没有等那种白痴老哥的必要!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶 这个土豆烧肉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是加了咖喱的土豆烧肉!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是苹果的秘方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 想不到味道很搭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为「咖喱要和重要的人一起吃」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「咖喱要和重要的人一起吃」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家是不放豌豆的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 现在不说更待何时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 荻野目同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很诚恳地求你帮个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在观察野鸟的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带着一本笔记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 那本笔记能借给我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用完了马上就还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说蠢话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我非借给你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 绝对不借你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 那也不是能随便借人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 那不过是单纯的日程记事本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你看过了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是偶然间瞄了一眼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只不过是些计划安排…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…话说 那都是你一厢情愿的空想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是…命运
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本笔记上 写着我的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的命运日记
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「命运日记」 这也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我已经老实交代了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来轮到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道那本笔记的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会需要它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是之前从那个水族馆买回来的纪念品?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太惊讶 好好听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 这帽子的真身是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星生命!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个外星生命 命令我们把你的笔记…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是日记弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果违抗命令的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你别开玩笑了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我当白痴吗 我可是很认真在听的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「命运日记」什么的 那才真叫莫名其妙好吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 「外星生命」又是什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脑袋不是坏掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存 战略!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine——!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告知你等必将一事无成之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 啥? 啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本打算默不作声听你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你这头母猪竟然肆意妄为胡言乱语
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀 阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 赶紧把你那不可救药的妄想排泄物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是那所谓的「命运日记」交给那边的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等 这什么呀这是!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬 你究竟是怎么了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:15:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子有问题的是你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个跟踪狂超变态女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬 你为什么要说那么过分的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呸 竟敢跟我顶嘴 真是让人恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个脑子烂透让人作呕的母猪婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太过分了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至于说到那个份上吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 下人 你也别在那发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧去把那日记抢过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 虽然你是下了命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她都掉下去了 我想抢不是也抢不到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人当白痴啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 你都做了什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是阳毬的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的卡车等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是顶帽子 太小题大做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那辆卡车!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 这一天怎么这么悲剧啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 给我停住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:21.25,flashback_br,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(300,0)}9年前 拂晓，台风过境之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:18.95,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}冠叶与爸爸。那是男子汉之间的约定。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.25,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}那是成功男人的脊梁。所以我。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠叶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上没有不会停息的暴风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果一直等到它停息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法保护重要的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘记了 冠叶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作起来 阳毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁开眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬…别死…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为那是顶普通的帽子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阳毬在开玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土豆烧肉呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 叔叔?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次说的钱 已经汇到你店子的账户里了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么来源不明的钱 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来我们就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以暂时住在这个家里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:54.67,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}5{\fs30\pos(640,630)}TH STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:54.67,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才要那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:24.50,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}おやじの靴を　はいてみた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:28.11,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}俺には　ちょっとキツイけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:31.86,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なかなか渋い音をだす
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:33.52,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stepping Slipping
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.51,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's my Daddy's shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:38.95,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}トンガリ靴　はいたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:42.55,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ヤツと町を歩いたら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:46.11,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}恥ずかしそうに　笑い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:47.79,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stepping　Slipping
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.62,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's my Daddy's shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:52.18,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうさ　これが　俺の
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:57.71,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}俺らの　おやじの靴さ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:01.47,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}擦り切れてて　キズだらけの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:04.81,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}古ボケた靴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:10.35,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}おやじの靴が　ひかりだし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:13.96,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今じゃ　一番お気に入り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:17.46,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ビルの谷間で踊りだす
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.12,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stepping Slipping
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:21.15,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's my Daddy's shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:22.82,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stepping Slipping
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:25.31,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's my Daddy's shoes
